                <REQUIREMENT UUID="x04000000001BE0BD">
                  <SHORT-NAME>EscEngineControlManagement</SHORT-NAME>
                  <CATEGORY></CATEGORY>
                  <NAME>EscEngineControlManagement</NAME>
                  <OWNED-COMMENTS/>
                  <TEXT>The management of engine speed control shall follow the following behavior. The sub-requirements will explain how to manage each state and transition.

Note: This state machine (and states and transitions defined after) is not an implementation requirement but only a behavior requirement.


Engine Speed Control Management state machine
</TEXT>
                  <FORMALISM></FORMALISM>
