ACC-H-048
ACC-H-054
or
ACC-B-049
ACC-B-058
nil referencenil referencenil reference
ACC_preset1_applied
HMI_AdaptiveCruiseControl
ACC-H-049
or
ACC-B-050
nil referencenil referencenil reference
ACC_preset2_applied
HMI_AdaptiveCruiseControl
ACC-H-050
or
ACC-B-051
nil referencenil referencenil reference
ASL_preset1_stored
HMI_AdjustableSpeedLimiter
ASL-H-017
ASL-H-022
or 
ASL-B-019
ASL-B-025
nil referencenil referencenil reference
ASL_preset2_stored
HMI_AdjustableSpeedLimiter
ASL-H-018
ASL-H-023
or 
ASL-B-020
ASL-B-026
nil referencenil referencenil reference
ASL_selected_speed
HMI_AdjustableSpeedLimiter
ASL-H-019
ASL-H-024
or
ASL-B-021
ASL-B-027
nil referencenil referencenil reference
ASL_preset1_applied
