                  <OWNED-COMMENTS/>
                  <TEXT>This function shall request a warning to be displayed for the driver when the ambient temperature moves into a range around freezing temperature.


The graph below is an example of how the activation and deactivation shall be done. The activation/deactivation temperatures in the graph is an example.


All activation and deactivation temperatures above shall be configurable.

At vehicle start it is not possible to determine if the temperature is raising or falling since there no historical ambient temperature data so separate conditions for activation of the function applies

