                </REQUIREMENT>
                <REQUIREMENT UUID="x04000000001BDA0D">
                  <SHORT-NAME>BehaviorDescription_EngineSpeedControlState</SHORT-NAME>
                  <CATEGORY></CATEGORY>
                  <NAME>BehaviorDescription_EngineSpeedControlState</NAME>
                  <OWNED-COMMENTS/>
                  <TEXT>As long as Engine Speed Control is enable or active (except Cross Country), an indication in the Construction page will be shown.

The following indication &quot;-- RPM&quot; shall be shown when Engine Speed Control is enabled but not active.

The following indication &quot;EngSpd RPM&quot; shall be shown when Engine Speed Control is active, showing the current value applied.

When the current target value has reached the maximum limit, an additional indication &quot;MAX&quot; shall be shown just above the target.

When the current target value has reached the minimum limit, an additional indication &quot;MIN&quot; shall be shown just above the target.</TEXT>
                  <FORMALISM></FORMALISM>
                  <URL></URL>
                  <MODE-REFS/>
                </REQUIREMENT>
                <REQUIREMENT UUID="x04000000001B8539">
                  <SHORT-NAME>BehaviorDescription_EngSpdCtrlNotAllowed</SHORT-NAME>
                  <CATEGORY></CATEGORY>
                  <NAME>BehaviorDescription_EngSpdCtrlNotAllowed</NAME>
                  <OWNED-COMMENTS/>
