</TEXT>
                  <FORMALISM></FORMALISM>
                  <URL></URL>
                  <MODE-REFS/>
                </REQUIREMENT>
                <REQUIREMENT UUID="x04000000001B606E">
                  <SHORT-NAME>BehaviorDescription_MuddySiteNotAllowed</SHORT-NAME>
                  <CATEGORY></CATEGORY>
                  <NAME>BehaviorDescription_MuddySiteNotAllowed</NAME>
                  <OWNED-COMMENTS/>
                  <TEXT>If one condition is not fullfilled to activate Muddy Site, a popup will be shown in the DID-display, indicating which condition is not met and how to proceed to fulfill this condition.

Note: Every popup in DID is combined with a sound. The level of the sound is depending on the severity of the popup.
</TEXT>
