                  <SHORT-NAME>BehaviorDescription_Driver1TimeRelatedStates_VM</SHORT-NAME>
                  <CATEGORY></CATEGORY>
                  <NAME>BehaviorDescription_Driver1TimeRelatedStates_VM</NAME>
                  <OWNED-COMMENTS/>
                  <TEXT>Exceeding driving time alert:
Warning to inform the driver that his cumulative driving time is near finished (4h15)

Exceeding driving time alarm:
Warning to inform the driver that he overtakes the madatory driving time (4h30)

Exceeding driving time adjustable alert:
The driver could adjust an additional alert to be informed X minutes before his cumulative driving time is over (4h30 of driving)</TEXT>
                  <FORMALISM></FORMALISM>
                  <URL></URL>
                  <MODE-REFS/>
                </REQUIREMENT>
                <REQUIREMENT UUID="x04000000001B2D5C">
